 * Question 3: What do you love about programming?
 *      The main reason why i love programming is because i really like solving problems-- and, well... quite frankly, that is mostly what coding is made of (from my experience and many others i have talked to).  I like looking at a problem and coming up with an "out of the box" (if you will) way of figuring it out.  Those are my main reasons.
